➜坟头蹦迪、死皮面霜、女奴对打，罗马人还有什么不敢玩的吗
http://www.sohu.com/a/414978360_624188	24915
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200826/985be52ce51a42f9b64163ea5541458b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在普通人眼中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>葬礼</strong>两个字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">光是提到就让人觉得——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200826/ee8109ecfd744aaaa909e5eb6d57c924.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直到几个月前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>黑人抬棺</strong>的视频横空出世</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才让大家知道——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>原来葬礼还能这么欢乐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但仔细想想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这不是和之前的坟头蹦迪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有着异曲同工之妙吗？</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>但要说起坟头蹦迪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那绝不是现代人的专利~</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200826/139e505d66074a56abf31720ef7286df.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">早在公元前12世纪的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>伊特鲁里亚文明时期</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就已经出现了类似这种</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“坟头蹦迪”</strong>的葬礼仪式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200826/8ae944284238442ea700468a14794d8a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和中国古代一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在当时的社会</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有地位的人死后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也会有<strong>殉葬</strong>的传统</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只不过这个殉葬仪式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和中国的比起来那真是刺激多了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">首先</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家会围在死者坟前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">进行<strong>沉重的哀悼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200826/b44dfd92197e43448071aadeba0a4cc9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哀悼结束后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">死者生前精心挑选的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>两位奴隶</strong>就会登场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在坟前为大家进行一场精彩的——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200826/e97202cdc8834d53b77ebd14cba4d01d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这场决斗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将以<strong>一方战死</strong>作为结束</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样不仅让死者在地下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多一个同行的伙伴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还能让参加葬礼的人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都能有个<strong>非常不错的观看体验</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在古罗马征服了伊特鲁里亚人后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样的传统还被延续了下来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200826/bdcb928042c0438aabde1ac6d5a61196.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古罗马人更是认为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这坟头蹦迪款格斗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅代表着<strong>死者的勇气与力量</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还能让<strong>死者灵魂得到净化</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">减轻通往冥界的痛苦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200826/db4bdb54442a4792a5aeb32be7efe373.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而在坟头格斗的<strong>次数</strong>以及<strong>规模</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还代表了<strong>死者的地位</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以只要钱够多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那你的葬礼上甚至可以格斗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>整</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有的贵族甚至还会安排<strong>女奴</strong>格斗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">久而久之</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这便逐渐延伸出了一种<strong>船新玩法</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——<strong>角斗士</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200826/21cd6741451b4fa1908e8fae370ab3b5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200826/c2fb332784064685ba392655870d3a13.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你一定很疑惑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这么血腥的东西为什么不仅能流传下来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还能演变出新的玩法儿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这些古罗马人都这么狼性的吗？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200826/603835125ba34b5cae25aea734794253.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">传说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在一个叫<strong>亚尔吧·龙加</strong>城市</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">国王被自个儿弟弟<strong>阿穆略</strong>篡了位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秉承着<strong>斩草要除根</strong>的理念</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阿穆略杀了国王所有的儿子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">留下了唯一的女儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">囚禁在<strong>贞女塔</strong>中做女祭司</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200826/51008dfd3b2541e8bc2434954ffd8a58.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">防火防盗防不住男人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">侄女还是和别人相爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生了两孩子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阿穆略一听——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200826/930c307794fe4b19a0cc61395c938496.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是抢走两孩子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丢进河里想淹死他们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可两孩子不仅没被淹死</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还被<strong>母狼</strong>发现了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看着送上门的两块鲜肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">母狼当即决定——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200826/7d0c3c603de341b8a69eac95be7215db.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">母狼用乳汁孕育了两孩子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直到一个<strong>牧羊人</strong>发现了他们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把他们带回家中抚养</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">取名<strong>罗慕洛</strong>和<strong>勒莫</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在悉心辅导下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两孩子经验值倍涨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后扶持了自个儿<strong>爷爷</strong>重回皇位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">…………</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200826/012ef0fddb86492ea3b7082ecc965ab0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">故事的结局并不像童话结局那样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爷孙从此过上了幸福快乐的生活</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两孩子反而有自己的想法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">决定去之前被救的地方建个<strong>新的城市</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那以为城市建好后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两兄弟就过上幸福美好的生活了？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200826/a61fc529f4334392a80d4785fdc4c832.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们因为<strong>命名权</strong>吵了起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">勒莫表示自己先看到<strong>6</strong>只秃鹫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁先谁就是天选之人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">罗慕洛表示自己看到<strong>12</strong>只秃鹫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁多谁才是天选之人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两人就此争执不下发生了格斗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">罗慕洛杀死了勒莫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用自己的名字给新城市命了名——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>罗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>马</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">连传说都这么狼性</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人民怎么能不<strong>狠一点</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这类打打杀杀的表演</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无疑才是大众喜闻乐见的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200826/2ba109b716b846edad07690a6e4c5e43.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在最开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是只属于<strong>贵族的快乐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟要买奴隶养奴隶办宴会</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后邀请一样无聊的贵族</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来观看血腥角斗比赛这事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是挺费钱的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且在那个时期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">角斗士基本得打到<strong>一方毙命</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才能结束</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200826/23b33d966eda40df9f3afa34dd43c358.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随着古罗马的日渐强大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人民富裕了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">角斗的次数越来越<strong>多</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">规模也变得越来越<strong>大</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至为了满足大众的观战欲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">建立了<strong>角斗场</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200826/b19cdb1d81d843979bcb50f50727d074.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算是看打打杀杀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那也得<strong>有来有回</strong>的才好看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一下就秒杀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或者上场就吓尿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这类全程是尿点的打斗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是没有观众会愿意看的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是<strong>角斗士表演培训学校</strong>由此诞生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而角斗士们也被分配了各种<strong>设定</strong>——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200826/142697cb7c2741dc8b8e0e0f24701ff1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有盾大头盔大还带匕首的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>矮大壮</strong>莫米罗角斗士</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200826/483f5f54db544e8ab44edae35c4f90b4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有只带小盾小匕首</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>几乎裸奔</strong>的色雷斯角斗士</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200826/2cdb3852a5cc4e56a8188fe8b2880f20.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有只穿皮制护肩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拿着网和三叉戟的<strong>闰土</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">网斗士</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200826/21887f0ed14049428f3c691cd941c314.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也有全副武装<strong>穿得最多</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只露两只眼睛的持盾剑斗士</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200826/0651eb015b4444a1aa418e4eeb5754a0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们将在班级里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>好</strong>（自）<strong>好</strong>（相）<strong>学</strong>（残）<strong>习</strong>（杀）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">争取为数不多的上角斗场的机会</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下好了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有专业的人去训练角斗士</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>培训费</strong>自然就不能少</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽说当角斗士大多都是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">社会地位低下的<strong>奴隶</strong>或者<strong>战俘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200826/bd49e33484344a3babd609f32edcffae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为给钱的老板</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能培养出一个能上角斗场参赛的角斗士</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅<strong>费时费力</strong>还很<strong>费钱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打一次就残了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或者死了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那是相当的不划算</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以从这时候开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">角斗士不用拼到死为止</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200826/a55d0c240f5c4bfda79e959ca9143cef.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">即便开始变成流行活动</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">举办一次角斗比赛依旧<strong>挺烧钱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以也不是天天都有得看的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而能有角斗比赛看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">基本都得靠<strong>贵族</strong>或者</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想要拉票的<strong>政治家</strong>承包</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时能承包一场角斗士比赛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅能受到<strong>底层平民欢迎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>提高家族威望、获得选票</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最重要是可以向别的富人们——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>炫</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>富</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200826/344e9d2e6bd84963b864b98b6540a529.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而为了能让更多的人看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">方便自己拉选票提高声誉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">角斗表演也变得更加<strong>戏剧化</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到这里你肯定就会说：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200826/2f06a1b071ef41b68f0ba8aa513cf62d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很遗憾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那是<strong>斗兽士</strong>的表演</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它和角斗士是<strong>两种不同的职业</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">斗兽士的历史没有角斗士那么长</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但<strong>残暴程度</strong>一点也不低于角斗士</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为他们不止有<strong>人打兽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至还有<strong>兽打兽</strong>的选项</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用来满足大家关于</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“百兽之王究竟是谁”的好奇心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200826/9231e5c5bce24eb6a6624032ea864647.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">观众们的最爱依旧是角斗比赛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以斗兽比赛通常都是用来<strong>暖场</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">压轴的依旧是角斗比赛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了满足观众们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">角斗士比赛开始<strong>打磨剧本</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后期的角斗表演在开始前会有<strong>剧情预告</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以及用<strong>“角斗明星”</strong>作为的噱头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吸引观众前来观赏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后到处跟团演出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200826/9989f9ec1f874dd4915b586b18844824.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这下比赛的角斗士们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然身为低微</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却靠着一身熟练技巧和勇气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成为全民pick的爱豆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吸了一票忠实粉丝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至有人在墙上刻字<strong>打call</strong>和<strong>表白</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200826/06129fdc9db4428e8ee0f41f48843fa8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而不少狂热女粉丝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还会抢购角斗士掉落的限量周边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——<strong>身体死皮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">做成<strong>面霜</strong>敷在脸上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并相信用完这个死皮面霜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就能变得更有魅力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200826/b3efa9889ddd40e4afa1882ce7aacc75.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了死皮面霜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有人血馒头同款</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——<strong>角斗士血药包</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由于角斗士的战力强大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们相信喝了他们的血能<strong>包治百病</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至还出现了卖血贩子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200826/d94f8f2492284bcfa020d2cc070c8b88.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随着角斗比赛越来越受欢迎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">下到普通人上到皇帝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都会自愿到角斗士学校里学习</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这不得不提——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古罗马帝国着名暴君</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>康茂德</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他最爱的运动就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">披着心爱的小斗篷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">下场去和角斗士们比赛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还宣称自己是大力神<strong>海格力斯</strong>的儿子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200826/d88b9a22c5fc42de9a927f766b718f5d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身为皇帝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天天工作不好好干就<strong>沉迷打架</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身边的人就看不过去了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们多次尝试<strong>暗杀</strong>康茂德</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200826/9231e5c5bce24eb6a6624032ea864647.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">康茂德<strong>幸运值点满了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">愣是几次暗杀都成功躲过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">思来想去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">暗杀者终于顿悟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人在高兴时候最容易放松警惕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是他们选择</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在康茂德从角斗场<strong>快乐摔♂跤</strong>后下手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那时的康茂德</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一定身体疲惫脑子空白</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只剩一个目标：泡热水澡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就趁他准备泡澡时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">假意递上一杯解乏的<strong>美味毒酒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再召唤出暗中等待的<strong>摔跤手</strong>给他来个惊喜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200826/0b01d50e92f04ab490905b71af735acd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本就疲惫的康茂德</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在毒酒和摔跤手的双重攻击下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无力反击</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最终死于自家澡堂中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而罗马帝国也因此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陷入了一连串混乱的内战之中……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说到这里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肯定会有人问了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">内战开始角斗士的命运会如何？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">传说中的斯巴达卡斯战役又是怎么回事？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而角斗士最终又是怎么走向没落的呢?</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200826/7c7c853769bf4d4cae139acd9daec6c4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">卖个关子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们下次一定——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200826/901337dd513442a08114570ca3206389.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200826/abf209160ed741889b807cec6e1a899d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>